Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美身体不要抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有伊织  手指
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓节奏慢了  快跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  动作要到位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次练习都要当作是正式演出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有要好好观察周围
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美  你知道刚才错在哪里了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后伊织是手指的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是伸直了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸直了啊  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.67,0:00:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再干脆点  这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是原偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  真不愧是{\fs26}原{\r}偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把开头的三首过一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里三个人要步调一致
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美手低了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子真严格呢  律子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.47,0:01:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总觉得比平时更有干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要举办龙宫小町的秘密演唱会了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.04,0:01:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  我现在在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再从头来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有伊织  手指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  哪里不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是做了吗
