Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们四人真是要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚都肿了
